data.description: Now here's a charming 3bedroom,2 bath single story home located in the desirable Anatolia subdivision of Rancho Cordova. This almost 1,600sq.ft beautifully well maintained smart home, features a large kitchen with gorgeous granite counters with lots of cabinets to include pantry closet and stainless-steel appliances. Upgraded bathrooms with quartz sinks/showers, nice tile and laminate flooring, inside laundry room with washtub and cabinets, triple pane windows throughout with lots of upgrades and storage space. Big backyard with two large storage sheds, fruit trees, gardening area with little gazebo that's perfect for entertaining! Nice home with AWESOME curb appeal...
